<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>{{ membershipType }} Membership Discount</title>
        <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background: #0073e6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .discount {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e60000;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .price-details {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555555;
        }
        .old-price {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            color: #999999;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #0073e6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #005bb5;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777777;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 8px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 8px;
        }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">Discount on {{ membershipType }} Membership!</div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>Hi {{ firstName }},</p>
                <p>We have a **new offer** on our **{{ pricePlan }} Plan** for the **{{ membershipType }} Membership**.</p>
                <div class="discount">Save {{ discountPercentage }}% Today!</div>
                <div class="price-details">
                    <p>
                        <span class="old-price">€{{ oldPrice }}</span> → <strong>€{{ discountedPrice }}</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <p>Don't miss out! Upgrade your membership today and enjoy exclusive benefits.</p>
                <a href="{{ subscribeUrl }}" class="cta-button">Subscribe Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="footer">
                If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.
                <br>
                © 2024 Edge Tech. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
